            <field>
              <name>dev_nc_store_early_ret</name>
              <description>It is to control the core to treat the device and non-cacheable region store is non-blocking (earlier return) or blocking.&lt;br&gt;1: device and non-cacheable region store is non-blocking.&lt;br&gt;0: device and non-cacheable region store is blocking.</description>
              <bitOffset>24</bitOffset>
              <bitWidth>1</bitWidth>
              <access>read-write</access>
            </field>
            <field>
